      "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body" : "After reading\r\nhttps://github.com/isocpp/CppCoreGuidelines/issues/222 and\r\nhttps://github.com/isocpp/CppCoreGuidelines/issues/1707\r\nI decided to use a reference instead of a pointer because the member cannot/must not be nullable.",
